      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. everything is just... dying. the weather, the forests, everything. it feels like we're just watching a slow motion train wreck and there's nothing anyone can actually do to stop it. what's even the point of trying to build a life or a future when the foundation is literally crumbling?",
