      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"small action\" stuff just feels like a lie people tell themselves to sleep at night. It's just delaying the inevitable. If the planet is actually heading toward a collapse, then all this \"finding meaning\" is just decorating a sinking ship. It feels more like a huge waste of energy to keep pushing forward when the math just doesn't add up. It's like, why bother being part of this if it's all just going to end in misery anyway?",
